Arsene Wenger feels the introduction of VAR has exposed the law in its current guise as being loaded in favour of defenders. He wants to re-write offside law in a bid to end VAR controversy. [<br />
@MirrorFootball<br />
]<br />
<br />
''I am in the middle of the controversial situation with VAR and it is clear that the most difficult thing that people have with it is the offside rule.<br />
You have had offsides by a margin of a fraction of a centimetre, offside literally by a nose.''
